Mexican authorities tracked down and killed “El Mencho”, one of the world’s most wanted drug traffickers, by following a romantic partner to his safe house near a picturesque mountain town, the country’s defence secretary has revealed.

clusters.title: Trump Criticizes Supreme Court Justices Over Tariff Ruling
clusters.summary: Former President Donald Trump expressed his anger towards six Supreme Court justices following their decision to reject his tariffs. This ruling marks a significant legal setback for Trump, who has been vocal about his discontent with the court's stance. The incident highlights ongoing tensions between Trump and the judiciary, particularly regarding trade policies.
